Jeb Wormwood is a villager of Witchaven and can be found north of Witchaven near Caroline and Holgart. He can take players who have started the Slug Menace quest to and from the Fishing Platform.

Like most of the other Witchaven villagers, he succumbs to sea slug control after Slug Menace. If you haven't started the quest, he will simply say, "Hello there!"

Roles[edit | edit source]

Jeb will transport players to the Fishing Platform after Slug Menace, as Mayor Eustace Hobb confiscated Holgart's boat and gave it to Jeb.
